headline: Astronics and Avnet have been highlighted as Zacks Bull and Bear of the Day
summary: Zacks names Astronics its Bull of the Day on strong estimate revisions and growth momentum, while Avnet is tagged Bear of the Day as earnings expectations drift lower.

headline: Fewer burritos, more bargains: Consumers flash holiday warning signs
summary: In the coming week, some of the biggest names in retail, including Walmart, Target, Gap and Home Depot will report their latest earnings.
